{"tid":1873130,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"久保建英遭馬略卡助教扮「矇豬眼」歧視","createTime":"2020-02-10T12:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T20:54:52.000Z","uid":34899,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"da2e5b2fa501366e49b5ba19d3c1fa4525b93492","tid":1873130,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:50:24.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】日本國腳久保建英周日疑似遭對手一名助教種族歧視，令人側目。<br />\n<br />\n西甲護級球隊馬略卡於周日聯賽對愛斯賓奴，戰至65分鐘，久保建英後備入替，最終作客小負0:1，但賽果卻非比賽焦點。電視鏡頭可見，18歲小將久保建英在場邊熱身時，一名馬略卡助教作出「矇豬眼」的動作，引起前者注意，而這動作在西方世界，一般被視作歧視亞洲人的行為。<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後引起網民圍剿，馬略卡現時尚未作出回應，但相信獲悉後會作出處罰。再者，久保建英是皇家馬德里借將，若馬略卡拒絕處罰助教的話，恐怕會導致兩支球隊的關係轉差。<br />\n<br />\n久保建英借到馬略卡，上陣時間不少，至今披甲10場射入1球，預料他有機會代表日本出戰今年東京奧運。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qiiAyc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqiiAyc1.jpg&h=2f50e63b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=28479714263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fmobileweb%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D28479714263&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4XlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=cdb4c43d\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=28479714263</a>"},{"pid":"30bee4b6a39525506005fc769cba29f2dc8f1686","tid":1873130,"uid":207553,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:52:40.000Z","msg":"無女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b49d087ea091330cbeb79f023c4a5bbc8670f9","tid":1873130,"uid":5378,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:52:53.000Z","msg":"白鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201c753747cb6309a71f9d446452b01ef46053b5","tid":1873130,"uid":60562,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:55:1